Package: sqshr
Type: Package
Title: R interface to SQL Server on top of Sqsh
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yuri Possokhoff
Maintainer: Yuri Possokhoff <possokhoff@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows you to send SQL-queries to Microsoft SQL Server
    and represent the output as data.table. Leverage of Sqsh is useful for Linux
    users who meet inconvenience using ODBC for SQL Server connections.
License: GNU General Public License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports: data.table
